-- MOVES-Northern Trust names Hodgson senior director of GFO in EMEA
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Fri Sep 26, 2014 10:41AM EDT
-- None



Sept 26 (Reuters) - Custody bank Northern Trust Corp <NTRS.O> named Lesley Hodgson as senior director of its Global Family and Private Investment Offices (GFO) group in Europe, the Middle East and Africa (EMEA).

Hodgson, to be based in London, will report to Daniel Lindley, managing director of GFO, EMEA. Northern Trust said Hodgson will manage the client service teams in London and Guernsey.